1) Open The project with an IDE (Netbeans, Intellij)
2) build project with Maven
3) Download Tomcat 8
4) Copy target/iot-1.0-SNAPSHOT.war under tomcat/webapps/ROOT.war
5) Install and start MySql
6) create user and password (default_user="iotapp", default_password="eniso2021")
7) create database (default_database="iot_app")
8) give all permissions to the user for the database
9) start tomcat
